{"tid":1554573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理飛哂馬日】 9月15日國際民主日","createTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:45:36.000Z","uid":80972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"daf438589795539c76a12155a42063fe58d212d5","tid":1554573,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"近日好多臥狗滲入搞事，分明都係想我地分化勇武同和理飛，同埋喺國際社會面前醜化香港示威。<br />\n<br />\n9月15日有聯合國力推嘅國際民主日，應該黎一次超級和理飛日，全港再次曬馬，俾香港再次喺國際社會展示和平示威者嘅一面。希望推到民陣/其他有號召力嘅機構幫手入紙搞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/events/democracyday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fevents%2Fdemocracyday%2F&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=b8bc2118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.un.org/en/events/democracyday/</a><br />\n<br />\n#勇武休息日<br />\n#全民捉臥狗日"},{"pid":"c929fd367119688b01815e03ef35321a90bd5cec","tid":1554573,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:40.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"3504e66235b394fb33afb834c794c3275cad78e3","tid":1554573,"uid":37929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"民陣已經入左紙搞915"},{"pid":"832b8612300e79cf0e3ffecd0526061f115e76f6","tid":1554573,"uid":276758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:35:03.000Z","msg":"入紙又係提早要你取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bf6673fa75c6695713548456eb42ce984a2fcc","tid":1554573,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"11d8bcb92e8f7e2d54dee24b22d029f841261df3","tid":1554573,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3504e66235b394fb33afb834c794c3275cad78e3","tid":1554573,"uid":37929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"民陣已經入左紙搞915"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"希望搞到"},{"pid"